{"tid":2173222,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"揭私隱危機 大狀︰DNA用途無界線","createTime":"2020-08-25T06:07:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T06:07:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4d7419bf3f689ea957c99f7da57788a4203cab8d","tid":2173222,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T06:07:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200825/R2S7XKRPJJFT5DEFN5G4G3NIFI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200825%2FR2S7XKRPJJFT5DEFN5G4G3NIFI%2F&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXVuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=a1c3bcda\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200825%2FR2S7XKRPJJFT5DEFN5G4G3NIFI%2F&h=1b47fd94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200825/R2S7XKRPJJFT5DEFN5G4G3NIFI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n揭私隱危機 大狀︰DNA用途無界線<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】林鄭政府力推全民檢測，市民擔心私隱因此外洩，本身為執業大律師的公民黨成員梁嘉善昨在facebook撰文，質疑全民檢測涉多項私隱外洩隱憂。梁直斥政府在抗疫問題上，處處盤算如何與北面接軌，「將抗疫問題『政治化』的，正正就是特區政府」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/enI-QtO927xCLrcC7LFs5buowCw=/1536x1024/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NAK3CDFP6VGU3D55M3V3PKEFFY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FenI-QtO927xCLrcC7LFs5buowCw%3D%2F1536x1024%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNAK3CDFP6VGU3D55M3V3PKEFFY.jpg&h=3f3da024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁嘉善（圖右）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中資控制 市民無從監察<br />\n<br />\n梁嘉善指出，政府聲稱收集的樣本僅作檢測病毒，「但檢測由中資公司控制」，運作無從監察。她續指，只要有DNA樣本的數據，科學上已可辨識一個人的身體狀況、特徵、甚至籍貫等，能確定個人身份，她擔心「檢測」只是政府的籠統字眼，「收集DNA後，用作統計、調查等全都可勉強說成『檢測』的一部份」，質疑政府釐清收集DNA用途的界線，似有實無。<br />\n<br />\n她又指，DNA樣本數據存放亦成疑，如樣本以電子化紀錄，「會儲存在哪個伺服器、伺服器又座落哪裏？」。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n負責統籌普及社區檢測計劃的公務員事務局局長聶德權只重申，。。。。。。。。"}]}